ODM party has resolved to handpick the candidate that will fly the party 's flag in the coming Migori senatorial by-election slated for 8th of October. According to the party chairman John Mbadi, given the strict timelines issued by the IEBC, the party will not have adequate time to conduct party primaries in the county. Meanwhile, ANC party leader Musalia Mudavadi has differed with Ford Kenya party leader Moses Wetangula over claims that NASA was dead. Mudavadi insists that the NASA coalition is there to stay.